{"tid":1001921,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"見到身邊啲fd開始有囡囡，有感而發","createTime":"2019-01-30T13:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T20:03:24.000Z","uid":87515,"like":40,"dislike":270,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4af327dd47d715e24bdc0cf5e52284c6f03f82","tid":1001921,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"身邊啲fd個個都係物以類聚，肥矮柒毒至少中兩種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個無論外表定行為，一睇就知係一等一既毒男<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲係中學同大學都識到囡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾次佢地話約出黎食飯<br />\n<br />\n一見到面即刻Hi咗出聲，原來個個都係食豬扒同醜女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個仲係食二手西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常啲靚菜唔會睇得上毒男，但係豬扒肥西把尺其實同港女一樣，理應唔會考慮毒男<br />\n<br />\n同樣道理，毒男個把尺至少度下啲正常樣既囡囡，以前識班fd個陣，大家都一齊笑下啲肥西，睇下啲靚既cosplay雞，咁至少我覺得大家啲標準都唔會差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁到底係佢地鳩痕西痕，是但搵件就手，定係饑不擇食到呢個程度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係萄葡佢地有囡，要我日日對住暗瘡肥婆，咁我寧願單身一世"},{"pid":"66d0bc56f32d354733cf1504a49fe28ee64d414c","tid":1001921,"uid":64374,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T14:00:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"404a5ca0c50f6dc4d71f019a0ad67fb8b7d97b6c","tid":1001921,"uid":206802,"like":344,"dislike":9,"score":335,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"淨係識用外表睇人<br />\n抵你一世無女"},{"pid":"580c7ba17dbda026baf88496d2c8997d2d094fcf","tid":1001921,"uid":17232,"like":9,"dislike":62,"score":-53,"quote":{"pid":"404a5ca0c50f6dc4d71f019a0ad67fb8b7d97b6c","tid":1001921,"uid":206802,"like":344,"di